snippet.title: Gameological Dig
snippet.description:
A Declaration:
Welcome to Gameological Dig, a channel devoted to playing games with obtuse and interesting stories. The aim of this channel is to treat these game worlds like an archeological site, meant to be unearthed and studied, so that we may better understand their plots, characters and themes. 

Check Out our sister Channel "Indie Mages" here:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC_o3W4WP1Jf0hPLaYsQfuGQ
